rows.label: qst202209_msg0003
rows.name:
I'm looking for a boy. I kinda
shocked him by accident before...
Any idea where he might be?

rows.label: qst202209_msg0004
rows.name:
Oh hey, you're the sparky girl
everyone's going on about.

rows.label: qst202209_msg0006
rows.name:
Yeah. You go around catching bad kids
and zapping them with lightning, right?

rows.label: qst202209_msg0007
rows.name:
Doesn't really bother me, though.
I know I've been good.

rows.label: qst202209_msg0009
rows.name:
Uh, wait, no no, that's all wrong!
Don't worry, I'd never do anything
like that!

rows.label: qst202209_msg0010
rows.name:
Anyway, can you tell me about
the boy?

rows.label: qst202209_msg0011
rows.name:
Mmm...I only know what my mum told
me. I don't really know him proper.
